She called that night. Asked
me to give you a message.

106
00:07:11,197 --> 00:07:13,370
She said she was pregnant.

107
00:07:15,969 --> 00:07:19,712
Which, God and Planned
Parenthood willing,

108
00:07:19,773 --> 00:07:23,084
