gonna be a nightmare.

221
00:14:17,023 --> 00:14:18,798
What if he's a good kid?

222
00:14:18,858 --> 00:14:22,806
He's a kid. Best you can hope
for is he's a nightmare.

223
00:14:22,895 --> 00:14:27,037
House, I'm not naive. I realize that
this thing could go very badly,

224
00:14:27,133 --> 00:14:30,979
but the point is my son wants to
meet me, and I want to meet him.

225
00:14:58,664 --> 00:15:00,541
Popo, I presume.

226
00:15:06,372 --> 00:15:09,751
